data.description: RECENT PRICE REDUCTION! Cul-de-sac, backs up to conservation and has easement, on the right side of the property. Access to walking trails and nature trails. Quiet fenced in backyard, with view and access to a private pond and fishing dock. Solid block to roof. Beautiful community pool in the neighborhood as well! 15 miles to Cocoa Beach, 35 miles to Kennedy Space Center. 50 miles to Disney and Universal. 30 miles to Orlando International Airport 8 miles to downtown Historic Cocoa Village.
